{"tid":938230,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱食完m記嗰新批 正呀!!!","createTime":"2018-12-12T06:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T10:23:13.000Z","uid":207990,"like":3,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"79b6e515150994d0b5feb866c90f1e2c9ad7569c","tid":938230,"uid":207990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:53:47.000Z","msg":"頭先諗住食m記嗰個雙層巨無霸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點知見到有嗰新批<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  具有冒險精神嘅我當然要試試佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點知竟然唔伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  芝士同藍莓嘅配搭 一黑一白 好比天使與魔鬼 差少少出現幻覺 咁凍嘅天氣食 個批再加幾分 令到嗰雙層巨無霸都變配角<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過我覺得食得多會膩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 中立非打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我估一定會有人話我平時食開屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e3fe4c31bd48fe740d3879ad9840340316184aa","tid":938230,"uid":207990,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:09:59.000Z","msg":"點解要負皮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f439ea1af018e992427fdf8e91a13474b3159f","tid":938230,"uid":161462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e3fe4c31bd48fe740d3879ad9840340316184aa","tid":938230,"uid":207990,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:09:59.000Z","msg":"點解要負皮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:10:20.000Z","msg":"無圖"},{"pid":"9792cb762f008f6a24152d090ec8b8a154192e95","tid":938230,"uid":207990,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"e6f439ea1af018e992427fdf8e91a13474b3159f","tid":938230,"uid"